    "While methods to artificially generate multi-fidelity data with desired fidelity correlations have recently been proposed 63, we did not pursue this direction as remarkably large collections of real-world multi-fidelity data are available, covering a large range of fidelity correlations and diverse chemical spaces.",
    "Furthermore, the successful application of such techniques to molecular data is yet to be demonstrated.",
    "Nature Communications | (2024) 15:1517"
  ],
